Title: Self-dual vortices in a Maxwell-Chern-Simons model with non-minimal

couplingAuthors: H.R. Christiansen, M.S. Cunha, J.A. Helayel-Neto, L.R.U. Manssur,

A.L.M.A. NogueiraComments: 12 pages, 9 figures, 2 tables; some typos corrected, one reference

updated. To be published in the Int. J. Mod. Phys. A (1999)Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A14 (1999) 1721-1736

We find self-dual vortex solutions in a Maxwell-Chern-Simons model withanomalous magnetic moment. From a recently developed N=2-supersymmetricextension, we obtain the proper Bogomol'nyi equations together with a Higgspotential allowing both topological and non-topological phases in the theory.